Description:
Oasis Village - Perfect community living
Positioned in Oasis Village this three bedroom home has been lovingly cared for and is quite generous in size. The open plan living has kitchen overlooking a separate meals and a spacious lounge. The kitchen has walk in pantry, electric wall oven and gas cooktop. All three bedrooms have built in robes and ceiling fans. The bathroom has a shower, vanity and a separate toilet. Climate is controlled by reverse cycle split system in the lounge area. Externally there is a double tandem garage with remote control access, screened outdoor entertaining area, small garden shed and low maintenance rear yard. To keep the electricity bills to a minimum there is also an 8 panel solar electricity unit. Oasis Village is set in beautiful landscaped surrounds and gives retirees the freedom and independence they deserve. Facilities include in-ground swimming pool, tennis court, recreational hall and so much more. It even has permanent storage area for caravans (subject to availability). It is conveniently located less than 2km from the CBD and has walking tracks directly into town and also has public bus transport coming through on a regular basis.
